{"tid":1785636,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"訛稱能醫百病 內地「能量水」騙6.7億","createTime":"2019-12-16T13:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T14:33:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b123e162513c62f8c28dc231561f5717ef29ebf3","tid":1785636,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191216/HQDD2KMSHTFUCLWTTNXZTBA3YI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191216%2FHQDD2KMSHTFUCLWTTNXZTBA3YI%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7v4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=ab8b771c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20191216%2FHQDD2KMSHTFUCLWTTNXZTBA3YI%2F&h=35e60983\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20191216/HQDD2KMSHTFUCLWTTNXZTBA3YI/</a><br />\n<br />\n訛稱能醫百病 內地「能量水」騙6.7億<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191216/large/1576426356_9695.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576426356_9695.gif&h=d26ad497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n騙倒無數人的神奇水號稱能醫百病。<br />\n<br />\n中國的騙局層出不窮，近日央視揭穿了一宗「SSG生命能量水」騙案，奸商聲稱該產品「能醫百病」，總共騙得六億元人民幣（下同‧6.7億港元）。央視發現，所謂能量水只是鹽加地下水。<br />\n<br />\n賣水公司聲稱，SSG生命能量水是被地殼運動封存起來的遠古海洋之水，當地人稱為「神水」，獲多個中美權威機構認可，不但可以逆轉衰老、延長壽命，甚至能治百病。公司又聲稱，創辦人的臉被硫酸燒傷，只需連續七天飲用能量水即可恢復如初。公司更提供漂浮艙，倒入能量水後，客人浸泡在水內，達到治療保養的效果。央視走訪「能量水」的採集地，發現能量水只是鹽含量較高的地下水源。至於漂浮效果，是因為加鹽的水密度很高，足以承托人體。而治療重病的功效，更是子虛烏有。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n層壓式推銷 六萬人中招<br />\n<br />\n全中國約有六萬人中招，合共被騙去六億元人民幣。部份人士更是貪字得個貧，原因是公司賣水是傳銷服務，該公司更推出自家虛擬貨幣，一個虛擬貨幣等於30元（33.5港元），如果購買12萬元能量水，即可獲得3,200個虛擬貨幣，兌換人民幣則是9.6萬元（10.7萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n央視"},{"pid":"cb9d68b821c709380734ebe5ee46fbaedbab115b","tid":1785636,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pie4mpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPie4mpm.jpg&h=4cc5750a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=f485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a&amp;oe=5EAED219\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3Df485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a%26oe%3D5EAED219&h=70a59658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"622b625075514b8a063efe16870ceb1c05439bb9","tid":1785636,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:59:46.000Z","msg":"同以前隻鑽石能量水一9樣<br />\n人類總是"},{"pid":"dbcf150c5f0c10fdf5b9b04e70927a0d4eedb6a5","tid":1785636,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T14:03:15.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">德國戰線要人</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標：5萬人聯署</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">依家差2萬人咋！！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6935